Quick tips:
 * Shift+Enter opens the selected item in a new tab
 * Option+Enter searches the typed string on google
 * There are special commands to add and remove bookmarks (try typing add or remove)
 * There's also a special command to use Cmd+J on websites where Cmd+K is used (try typing "Use Cmd")
 * It is also possible to disable the extension altogether for the current domain (try typing disable)
 * The extension does not open when there's selected text (to avoid conflicting with some applications shortcuts).
